name: The Awesome Shirt
description:
This shirt is a top of the line American Apparel Tee. Silkscreened design is a dog, taking a poo, with old-school stripper stars covering the unmentionables, and the eyes.

This is a one of a kind design created by a man with photoshop and an unhealthy love of his deceased dog. In our mind, that translates to "Totally worth it".

While supplies last!

This week only, SHIPPING IS FREE! (in the continental North Carolina)
